Two days earlier, Shane had flown to the UK where he visited his ex-fiancee at the £6million Herefordshire mansion they bought in 2012.

Warne and Miss Hurley spent the night there before travelling to London and spending a second night together at her townhouse.

They were believed to be trying to rekindle their relationship, with Warne recently hinting they were on the verge of a reconciliation.

