But the Australian is said to have visited Michelle at lunchtime the following day, apparently taking champagne and roses to her £500-a-night eighth-floor suite.

The pair emerged separately four hours later, with the underwear firm boss heading to the BBC’s central London office to appear on Radio 5Live show, On The Money.

Michelle, who divorced ex-husband Michael in January last year, flew back to Scotland the next day, while Warne jetted to Las Vegas to take part in a poker tournament.

