The mother-of-three was at home in her luxurious Glasgow townhouse on Sunday.

She cancelled a speaking engagement at the Scottish Wedding Show, on behalf of her lingerie company Ultimo, where she was due to appear at 2pm. Mone, who was at the two-day event on Saturday, was said to be ill.

Shane is not the first sportsman to be linked to Mone. In 2012 married footballer Robbie Savage was seen leaving her home in the early hours following an award ceremony earlier that evening. The pair claimed they are just friends.

